HEADWORD: Lionize
<hw>Li"on*ize</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧"⟦ucr⟧n*⟦imac⟧z)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Lionized</conjf>
